format of comment /* add CSS here */ 

HTML Comment format 
<!-- This is a comment -->
<div class="example">Words, words, words.</div>

Tag Selector Quiz: Which paragraph(s) would be affected? 
p {
  text-align: right;
}
Answer: all paragraphs

Attributes and Selectors: 
class can be added to multiple elements 
ids can only be used once per page 

Tag Selector
h1 {
  color: green;
}
class Attribute Selector
.book-summary {
  color: blue;
}
id attribute selector
#site-description {
  color: red;
}

Selectors Quiz: which HTML elements match the given CSS statement? 
.right {
   text-align: right;
} 
1. <div class="right"></div> 
2. <a href="#" class="leftright"></a>
3. <button id="right"></button>
4. <p class="highlight module right"></p>
Answer: 1 and 4 
order of classes do not matter and multiple classes can be added as long as there is a space between 

CSS References Quiz: Use CSS References to answer the questions below 
1. What CSS property is used to italicize text? font-style
2. What CSS property is used to underline text? font-decoration
3. What CSS property is used to uppercase text? font-transfor
4. What CSS property is used to bold text? font-weight 

CSS units: absolute and relative 
absolute: px, mm, in, cm
relative: %, em, vw, vh 

Units in CSS Quiz: Add the following changes to the website
<!DOCTYPE html>

<!-- Instructions: Add the following changes to this webpage:

* set the first div's width to 100px (pixels)
* set the second div's height to 200px (pixels)
* set the third div's margin to 1em
* set the fourth div's font-size to 2em

-->

<html>
<head>
    <title>Quiz - Units in CSS</title>
    <style>
    	.first {
            width: 100px;
    	}
    	.second {
            height: 200px
    	}
    	.third {
            margin: 1em
    	}
    	.fourth {
            font-size: 2em
    	}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="first"></div>
	<div class="second"></div>
	<div class="third">Hammock ex plaid nulla. Nihil stumptown gastropub, dreamcatcher gochujang franzen cillum cliche keffiyeh pop-up pug small batch knausgaard. Fanny pack elit you probably haven't heard of them before they sold out. Sint elit tofu et veniam irony 3 wolf moon. VHS slow-carb trust fund chartreuse wolf. Qui sed dreamcatcher cronut, hoodie fixie normcore. Gochujang dolor consectetur post-ironic.</div>
